<br>
The women that succeed in business are the ones that don't have children.<br>
<br>
Just like men that succeed in business these women choose to put their careers first.  they are available for late night sessions, they don't take months at a time off for maternity leave.  They don't need time off to go to junior's little league game or soccer match.<br>
