<br>
Choose.  The kids or the job.<br>
<br>
If you choose the kids, then you won't ever be a big business man or woman.  You'll languish somewhere in the middle.  Find a nice non-competitive job and be happy there.  Work enough to provide for your family and then spend as much time as possible with that family, you'll be happier.<br>
