You are suddenly missing from your job for months at a time.<br>
<br>
Guess what?  A man is going to be zooming in on that promotion while you're away and practically forgotten.<br>
<br>
It's the way things work.  You want to be competitive give up on the kids and go for it tiger...  You'll succeed.<br>
<br>
It's not about sexism anymore Jade.  It's who can do the job the best, devote the most time, be there when they are needed.<br>
<br>
Most women WILL NOT place their career ahead of children.<br>
<br>
That's a fact. <p>~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~<br>
